---

## 🚀 Step 7: **ONE-COMMAND GITHUB UPLOAD** - `deploy.sh`

Ye sabse important hai! Bas ek command aur sab kuch GitHub par chala jayega.

### 🪟 **Windows ke liye - `deploy.bat` banao:**

```batch
@echo off
echo ========================================
echo   ShadowTrap GitHub Auto-Deploy
echo ========================================

set /p commit_msg="Enter commit message: "

git add .
git commit -m "%commit_msg%"
git branch -M main
git push -u origin main

echo.
echo ✅ Successfully pushed to GitHub!
pause